{"tid":2423992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張華峰：昨天下跌一千多點，這一定是加印花稅引起的。　陳茂波：現在的指數升了600多點，股票市場波動常有。","createTime":"2021-02-26T08:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T10:06:12.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e40866fd269e3fe75f5e970aede20dfe13975ffb","tid":2423992,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T08:56:04.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n財政預算案建議股票印花稅增加三成，股市一度大瀉過千點，有立法會議員批評得不償失。財政司司長陳茂波指，近年推動互聯互通同股不同權等改革，股市成交額倍升非靠印花稅。<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員(金融服務界)張華峰：「昨天下跌一千多點，蒸發了數千億元，這一定是加印花稅引起的。」<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波：「就算不收印花稅，假如我們不改革，這些公司不能來香港上市，股票市場也沒現時興旺、繁榮、蓬勃的現象。星期三股市下跌不止香港，你看看日本、韓國、上海，下跌幅度最多3%，現在的指數升了600多點，股票市場波動常有。」點，股票市場波動常有。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=425279\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425279&d=6DLEtCU0DjtZYWozPjwd66crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=5f1da6d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425279&h=8fbc9f9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=425279</a>"},{"pid":"e67ee0df3a4ff8030bcd7f64eedb37634147df66","tid":2423992,"uid":180851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"波哥真攬炒唔係講玩<br />\n又送錢比人移民 又搞9港股"},{"pid":"36ebd859090a91fdd1cd5381fd951cc53298aa38","tid":2423992,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:05:30.000Z","msg":"穿撚埋2萬9<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a40232ec04fe00daebc3af5a07961de0f877f422","tid":2423992,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T10:06:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dr